OL,3,CSuspension of senior police figures a
OL,4,C'huge knock' admits acting top officer
OL,6,FThe suspension of three of the most
OL,7,Fsenior members of Gloucestershire
OL,8,FPolice has left the force in "unusual
OL,9,Fcircumstances", the Interim Chief
OL,10,FConstable has admitted.
OL,12,FMaggie Blyth became Gloucestershire
OL,13,FPolice's interim Chief Constable,
OL,14,Ffollowing the suspension of Rod Hansen
OL,15,Fafter allegations of gross misconduct
OL,16,Fwere made, pending an investigation.
OL,18,FThe force's Chief of Staff, Gary
OL,19,FThompson, has also been suspended over
OL,20,Fthe same incident.
