OL,4,C'huge knock' admits acting top officer
OL,6,FChief Constable Rod Hansen would have
OL,7,Fbeen replaced by his deputy Shaun
OL,8,FWest, but he is currently under
OL,9,Fcriminal investigation in relation to
OL,10,Fassault and misconduct in public
OL,11,Foffice.
OL,13,FThe force had been without a chief or
OL,14,Fa deputy for two weeks before Ms Blyth
OL,15,Fbegan her role on 22 October, after
OL,16,Fbeing seconded from the College of
OL,17,FPolicing.
OL,19,FIt is only the second time in the
OL,20,Fforce's 185-year history that a woman
OL,21,Fhas been at the helm.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
