OL,3,CSuspension of senior police figures a
OL,4,C'huge knock' admits acting top officer
OL,6,F"These are unusual circumstances,"
OL,7,Finterim Chief Constable Maggie Blyth
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"But actually, in terms of the day-to-
OL,11,Fday work that our staff and frontline
OL,12,Fofficers do, that continues very much
OL,13,Fon the normal trajectory."
OL,15,FDespite the challenges, Blyth - who
OL,16,Fhas more than 30 years of experience
OL,17,Fin policing - believes people in
OL,18,FGloucestershire do not need to worry.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
