OL,6,FShe said: "Trust and confidence are
OL,7,Fparamount to my role as Interim Chief
OL,8,FConstable.
OL,10,F"I can give absolute assurance to our
OL,11,Fcommunities today that our 999 calls
OL,12,Fare answered in the same way, and all
OL,13,Fcrimes are investigated in exactly the
OL,14,Fsame way.
OL,16,F"That continuity of service will, I
OL,17,Fhope, give the trust and confidence
OL,18,Fthat the organisation will continue as
OL,19,Fit always has done".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
