OL,4,C'huge knock' admits acting top officer
OL,6,FAside from policing, another concern
OL,7,Ffor Blyth's force - as with many
OL,8,Fforces - is tight budgets and the need
OL,9,Fto make savings.
OL,11,FGloucestershire Police is now paying
OL,12,Ftwo Chief Constable salaries. But
OL,13,Fasked if she is concerned about the
OL,14,Fforce's budget, Blyth said
OL,15,F"Gloucestershire is no different from
OL,16,Fany other police force".
OL,18,F"All public services are facing budget
OL,19,Fcuts and financial challenges," she
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
