OL,3,CSuspension of senior police figures a
OL,4,C'huge knock' admits acting top officer
OL,6,F"But absolutely, one of my priorities
OL,7,Fis looking at our financial situation
OL,8,Fand looking at the savings we need to
OL,9,Fmake into next year, and looking at
OL,10,Fwhat that means."
OL,12,FMs Blyth was appointed Interm Chief
OL,13,FConstable by the police and crime
OL,14,Fcommissioner on a short-term basis.
OL,16,FThe Office of the Police and Crime
OL,17,FCommissioner said a recruitment
OL,18,Fprocess to appoint a Temporary Chief
OL,19,FConstable to lead the force over the
OL,20,Flonger term is currently ongoing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
